{
  "texts": [
    "First every BOL had to be manually entered into the system, which proved somewhat challenging.",
    "Data entry mistakes carried a considerable risk that would cause invoicing issues and cargo mishandling.",
    "Standardizing was further challenged by BOLs from several airlines arriving in numerous patterns and designs.",
    "Delays brought out by hand entering limited consumer updates and real-time shipping tracking.",
    "Controlling BOL processing without adding additional staff becomes increasingly difficult as shipment numbers rise and scalability problems arise."
  ]
}